snippet.title: Stick Shift (2 minute gameplay teaser, free game)
snippet.description:
Stick Shift is a a short autoerotic night-driving game about pleasuring a gay car. It is available RIGHT NOW for Windows / Mac OSX / Linux. For more info and download links: http://radiatoryang.itch.io/stick-shift

game by Robert Yang (@radiatoryang, http://debacle.us)
music is "Crybaby" by Davey and the Chains (http://daveyandthechains.bandcamp.com/), used with permission
